Title: Go Fish
Actors: V.S. Brodie, Guinevere Turner, T. Wendy McMillan, Migdalia Melendez
Plot: Max is a trendy, pretty, young lesbian, who is having trouble finding love. A friend sets her up with Ely, whom Max likes, but Ely is frumpy, homely, and older. Nor do they have much in common. Can Max learn to look past the packaging?
Production: Samuel Goldwyn Company, Can I Watch
